    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s clean, runs like a dream, and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road, you've found it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
