    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my favorite set of wheels, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road! It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super well-loved, so it's ready to jump right into your next adventure. It drives beautifully and looks great parked in the driveway, too. I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit features a fully operational high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Critical preventative maintenance has been performed, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox is paired with a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a well-damped suspension that preserves the model's signature handling dynamics. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the powertrain and drivetrain are in excellent working order, making this a prime candidate for a dedicated driving enthusiast.",
